fields.calculatedFormula:
IF
            (
            OR(ISBLANK(SM_Actual_Execution_Date_Time__c), ISBLANK(SM_Actual_Duration__c)), '',


            TEXT( FLOOR( (SM_Actual_Duration__c-SM_Actual_Execution_Date_Time__c)*24))

            & ":" &

            IF(CEILING(MOD( (SM_Actual_Duration__c-SM_Actual_Execution_Date_Time__c)  * 24 * 60, 60)) > 9, '', '0')
            & "" &

            TEXT(CEILING(MOD( (SM_Actual_Duration__c-SM_Actual_Execution_Date_Time__c)  * 24 * 60, 60)) )
            )

fields.calculatedFormula:
IF
            (
            OR(ISBLANK(SM_Date_Time_Incident_Started__c), ISBLANK(SM_Date_Time_Incident_End__c)), '',

            TEXT( FLOOR( (SM_Date_Time_Incident_End__c-SM_Date_Time_Incident_Started__c)))

            & "d " &

            TEXT( FLOOR(MOD((SM_Date_Time_Incident_End__c-SM_Date_Time_Incident_Started__c) * 24, 24)))

            & "h " &

            IF(CEILING(MOD( (SM_Date_Time_Incident_End__c-SM_Date_Time_Incident_Started__c) * 24 * 60, 60)) > 9 , '', '0')
            & "" &

            TEXT(CEILING(MOD( (SM_Date_Time_Incident_End__c-SM_Date_Time_Incident_Started__c) * 24 * 60, 60)) )

            & "m"
            )
